These are Puzzles for 6x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
There 2 different types of food: onion, orange
2 different pets are kept: lizard, turtle
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, satire
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, trance
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, aconite
1. the owner of the lizard is the person watching satire movies##1
2. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person eating orange##5
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the fan of trance##8
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the fan of trance##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite      | almond-milk |
| Food          | orange      | onion       |
| Pet         | turtle | lizard  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy     | satire      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa       | trance      |
| Flower         | aconite    | balloon-flower       |

